OL,3,C'Our lives have gone too': Grieving
OL,4,Cfamily of student stabbed in random
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe distraught family of a 22-year-old
OL,8,Fstudent who was stabbed to death
OL,9,Fwhilst travelling in Amsterdam say
OL,10,Fthey want to tackle knife crime in his
OL,11,Fmemory.
OL,13,FDanny Castledine, from , was on his
OL,14,Fway to a music festival in Belgium in
OL,15,FJune 2022 when he was stabbed 44 times
OL,16,Fin a random attack and left dying in
OL,17,Fthe street.
OL,19,FHis attacker was later jailed for 14
OL,20,Fyears for manslaughter in a Dutch
OL,21,Fcourt.
