OL,3,C'Our lives have gone too': Grieving
OL,4,Cfamily of student stabbed in random
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHis mother Alison, a headteacher, said
OL,8,Fthe devastating news had put the lives
OL,9,Fof their family on hold.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News: "It's not just
OL,12,FDanny thats gone it feels like our
OL,13,Fwhole lives have gone as well.
OL,15,F"The things we enjoyed the most,
OL,16,Fbirthdays, Christmas, family events,
OL,17,Fwe just tried to avoid them because
OL,18,Fthey have turned into the worst times.
