OL,3,C'Our lives have gone too': Grieving
OL,4,Cfamily of student stabbed in random
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"Your life is just ruined and you just
OL,8,Fcan't prepare for that. The longer it
OL,9,Fgoes on the harder it gets because you
OL,10,Fmiss him so much.
OL,12,F"Danny was the glue that held our
OL,13,Ffamily together, he was always doing
OL,14,Fthings, planning things."
OL,16,FDanny's sister Chloe, 22, said she
OL,17,Ffelt the same now as she did when her
OL,18,Fbrother died two years ago.
