OL,3,C'Our lives have gone too': Grieving
OL,4,Cfamily of student stabbed in random
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"It is so incredibly lonely and
OL,8,Fstrange without him, nothing can
OL,9,Freplace the relationship we had as
OL,10,Fsiblings.
OL,12,F"Danny has always been there
OL,13,Fthroughout my whole life and it still
OL,14,Fdoesn't seem real," she said.
OL,16,FThe family have set up the Danny C
OL,17,FFoundation which aims to educate
OL,18,Fpeople about the devastating
OL,19,Fconsequences of knife crime.
