OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"If the person who killed Danny hadn't
OL,8,Ftaken the knife out with him Danny
OL,9,Fwould 100 per cent be here and how
OL,10,Fmany people would have been better off
OL,11,F- me, my mum, my dad, his friends, a
OL,12,Fwhole community of people. It's never
OL,13,Fjust one person," said Chloe.
OL,15,FAlison Castledine said the family did
OL,16,Fnot want Danny to have died in vain
OL,17,Fand want to see children as young as
OL,18,Ften given lessons about knife crime.
